{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were building barracks in which they housed future refugees that they brought in the new transports.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because they were bringing them in to such an extent that they needed more and more and more place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is why they went through all the trouble to train people to erect all these barracks, but more of permanent structure, because they were done with brick.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ones before were just all out of wood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are in 1943 like towards the, I would say, fall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in 1942, I would say also about fall that I-- that I-- well, you know first, things-- were going around-- there were flying different kind of rumors until such a time that some of us went through the places where the Sonderkommando 1 would do the actual gassing.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had-- had the chance to-- they were still living with us at such a time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't until a later time that they completely took them away, and they were not able to stay with the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were quarantined.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They told us about these-- about these shower heads and all that stuff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they got a message from one to another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to remember than in the beginning, people had a hard time believing things like this, a little bit, until you had one guy coming back, like myself, and telling people, hey, I was covering a mass grave.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't tell me, I know what-- what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so little by little, it spread, until-- until everybody knew what's really going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always had a kapo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The kapos, in general I would say, to the greatest extent, in the largest majority, were all acting like these hardened criminals.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
